headline: Vietnam Organic Food Market Growth and Company Analysis Report 2025-2033 Featuring Danone, General Mills, Sprouts Farmers Market, Hain Celestial, Kroger, United Natural Foods and Dole Food Co.
summary: The Vietnam Organic Food Market is projected to grow from US$ 1.04 billion in 2024 to US$ 2.68 billion by 2033, with an 11.16% CAGR. Driven by rising demand for healthier, sustainable foods and government initiatives supporting organic agriculture, this growth reflects a national shift towards biodiversity and eco-friendly farming. headline: Wheaties Unveils Football MVP Jalen Hurts as the Newest Champion of the Iconic Orange Box
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, September 04, 2025--Wheaties announced today that its newest legendary orange box will feature Philadelphia quarterback and champion Jalen Hurts. From being a hometown hero to Big Game stand-out, Hurts exemplifies what it means to be a Wheaties Champion, uplifting his team and strengthening his community through service, youth mentorship and support for Philadelphia schools.
